{
  "page": "Pink Pavilion",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>According to <i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Chronicles_of_Longsister\" title=\"The Chronicles of Longsister\">The Chronicles of Longsister</a></i>, the <b>Pink Pavilion</b> was the personal pavilion of <a href=\"/index.php/Belthasar_Bolton\" title=\"Belthasar Bolton\">Belthasar Bolton</a>, a member of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Bolton\" title=\"House Bolton\">House Bolton</a> who took part in the <a href=\"/index.php/Rape_of_the_Three_Sisters\" title=\"Rape of the Three Sisters\">Rape of the Three Sisters</a>. It was allegedly made from the <a href=\"/index.php/Flaying\" title=\"Flaying\">flayed</a> skins of one hundred <a href=\"/index.php/Sistermen\" title=\"Sistermen\">Sistermen</a>. <a href=\"/index.php/North\" title=\"North\">Northern</a> accounts of the war do not mention this, nor other numerous atrocities alleged in accounts of the war written by men from the <a href=\"/index.php/Vale\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Vale\">Vale</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pink_Pavilion&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Vale.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403141700\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.009 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.010 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 96/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8534/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 312/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 58/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 537/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    5.520      1 -total\n 73.42%    4.053      1 Template:Ref\n 46.96%    2.592      1 Template:Ref/core\n 25.16%    1.389      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:32292-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403141700 and revision id 298876\n -->\n",
